description: Glossed token sequence pattern mining using middle_dictionary.json
narrative: Gloss gaps are systematically positioned (max enrichment 4.03x at par_start) and section-specific (gap rate range 6.2pp). 16 gaps involve morphologically distinct MIDDLEs (edit distance >2 from any glossed MIDDLE), suggesting these are not simple variants of known operations but potentially encode material-specific or context-specific information that the operational gloss system does not capture.

methodology.morphological_distinctiveness: Levenshtein distance >2 from any glossed MIDDLE
methodology.position_enrichment: Observed vs expected gap rate by position (line_start/end/mid/par_start)
methodology.section_specificity: Gap rate variation across B/H/S/T/C sections
methodology.pass_criteria: Max positional enrichment >1.5x AND section gap rate range >5pp
